videos.description: Baylor's Jake Lindsey threads a pass to Tristan Clark who completes the and-1 dunk.
videos.headline: Clark finishes at the rim plus the foul

videos.description: Baylor's Jake Lindsey lobs an inbound pass up to Mark Vital for a powerful alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: Vital slams an alley-oop off the inbound pass

videos.description: Chris Chiozza pulls up from way downtown to continue Florida's sharp shooting early.
videos.headline: Chiozza splashes Florida's seventh 3 of the first half

videos.description: Florida finishes the first half with its ninth 3-pointer of the half as KeVaughn Allen nails a 3 to beat the buzzer.
videos.headline: Allen drills a stepback 3 just before the halftime buzzer

videos.description: Chris Chiozza splits the Baylor defense and hits a layup plus the foul while falling to the floor.
videos.headline: Chiozza makes acrobatic reverse layup

videos.description: Florida's Kevarrius Hayes swats away a layup to set up Egor Koulechov for a transition layup.
videos.headline: Gators defense ignites fast-break score

videos.description: Florida head coach Mike White talks highly about how his team played on the defensive end, rather than how good of a shooting day it had.
videos.headline: Mike White proud of Florida's defense against Baylor

videos.description: ESPN's Allison Williams and Dick Vitale break down Florida's 81-60 win over Baylor as they dominate at both ends of the floor.
videos.headline: Gators' shooting, defense leads to big win over Baylor

videos.description: Chris Chiozza scores 20 points as No. 20 Florida defeats Baylor 81-60.
videos.headline: Florida hands Baylor third straight loss
